<P>
 "What's that?" the widow whimpered, lifting her head. 
</P>
<P>
 "That's one of those devils under the sheets," the undertaker explained. 
</P>
<P>
 "That he was," the widow brightened. "That he was." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Argus Hamilton * 
