 I launched into an impromptu, rambling discourse on the birds and the bees 
that I hoped was on the first-grade level. But I could tell by the frustrated 
look on her face that it wasn't.  
</P>
<P>
 Finally, exasperated, she thrust in front of me the Barney Club membership 
application she was filling out and implored: "Daddy! What do I put here where 
it says sex? An M or an F ?"  
